trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<CipherData>" name="<CipherData>" href=""></xref> element in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: 代表<xref uid="langword_csharp_<CipherData>" name="<CipherData>" href=""></xref>中 XML 加密項目。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The CipherData class represents the `<CipherData>` element in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: CipherData 類別代表`<CipherData>`中 XML 加密項目。

trans-unit.source: It is a required element that provides the encrypted data.
trans-unit.target: 它是必要的項目，提供加密的資料。

trans-unit.source: It must either contain the encrypted data as base64-encoded text of the `<CipherValue>` element, or provide a reference to an external location containing the encrypted data using the `<CipherReference>` element.
trans-unit.target: 它必須以 base64 編碼的文字包含加密的資料`<CipherValue>`項目，或提供包含加密的資料使用外部位置的參考`<CipherReference>`項目。

trans-unit.source: In many cases, you do not need to directly create a new instance of the CipherData class.
trans-unit.target: 在許多情況下，您不需要直接建立 CipherData 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>, <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>, and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> classes create instances for you.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>， <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>，和<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>類別為您建立執行個體。</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A CipherData object can have either a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference> property or a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A> property, but not both.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > CipherData 物件可以有<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference>屬性或<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A>屬性，但非兩者。</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference>
